OL,3,CLabour to stage Holyrood vote urging
OL,4,Cdisclosure of hospital communications
OL,6,FScottish Labour is set to hold a
OL,7,Fparliamentary vote on Wednesday to
OL,8,Fpressure the Scottish Government to
OL,9,Fauthorise the immediate full
OL,10,Fdisclosure on the Queen Elizabeth
OL,11,FUniversity Hospital scandal.
OL,13,FThe party is lodging a motion calling
OL,14,Fon ministers to publish and preserve
OL,15,Fall records connected to contaminated
OL,16,Fwater, the ventilation system, and
OL,17,Fwhat it says was the "premature
OL,18,Fopening" of the hospital, and
OL,19,Fsubsequent communications relating to
OL,20,Fthe handling of infection.
