OL,6,FThe Scottish Hospitals Inquiry, which
OL,7,Fheard closing submissions last week,
OL,8,Fexamined the design and construction
OL,9,Fof the Queen Elizabeth University
OL,10,FHospital and the Royal Hospital for
OL,11,FChildren, which are on the same campus
OL,12,Fin Glasgow.
OL,14,FIt was launched in the wake of deaths
OL,15,Flinked to infections, including 10-
OL,16,Fyear-old Milly Main in 2017.
