OL,6,FScottish Labour has also requested
OL,7,Finformation from the SNP on if any
OL,8,Femails, texts, letters, documents and
OL,9,Fother records from this time,
OL,10,Fincluding relevant WhatsApps and other
OL,11,Fmessages, have been deleted.
OL,13,FLabour leader Anas Sarwar said: "What
OL,14,Fhappened at the Queen Elizabeth
OL,15,FUniversity Hospital is the single
OL,16,Fbiggest scandal in the history of
OL,17,Fdevolution.
