OL,6,F"Families seeking answers have been
OL,7,Fblocked at every turn by powerful
OL,8,Fpeople trying to protect themselves `
OL,9,Fand whistleblowers have been
OL,10,Fintimidated and bullied for doing the
OL,11,Fright thing.
OL,13,F"The culture of secrecy and cover-up
OL,14,Fmust end, and those responsible must
OL,15,Fbe held to account.
OL,17,F"People have died and their families
OL,18,Fdeserve the truth ` and they deserve
OL,19,Fit urgently."
