OL,3,CLabour to stage Holyrood vote urging
OL,4,Cdisclosure of hospital communications
OL,6,FWhen the hospital was opened in 2015,
OL,7,FNicola Sturgeon was first minister,
OL,8,FJohn Swinney was her deputy and the
OL,9,Ffinance secretary, and Shona Robison
OL,10,Fwas health secretary.
OL,12,FDuring First Minister's Questions last
OL,13,FThursday, First Minister John Swinney
OL,14,Findicated he would be willing to
OL,15,Fpublish relevant documents.
OL,17,FScottish Labour said it will request
OL,18,Fthe information again during the
OL,19,Fdebate.
