OL,3,CLabour to stage Holyrood vote urging
OL,4,Cdisclosure of hospital communications
OL,6,FMr Sarwar continued: "John Swinney has
OL,7,Ffailed to come clean about what the
OL,8,FSNP Government knew, when it knew it,
OL,9,Fand what role it played in the
OL,10,Fpremature opening of this hospital.
OL,12,F"Sunlight is the best disinfectant.
OL,13,FJohn Swinney and his ministers must
OL,14,Fpublish and preserve all their
OL,15,Fcommunications from that time, so we
OL,16,Fcan establish once and for all whether
OL,17,Fit was negligence or criminal
OL,18,Fincompetence that got us here."
OL,20,FThe Scottish Government has been
OL,21,Fapproached for comment.
